TopicTitle: Crash on Startup - Modded with KSPRC and KerbalAlarmClock

Articles.Content:
Version - 0.90 Windows (Steam user)

Log file:https://www.dropbox.com/s/omb2327mfmyzhhm/output_log.txt?dl=0

Downloaded mods:

KSRPC v0.1.9.5

Kerbal Alarm Clock v3.2.3.0

Reproduction Steps:

Game crashed on startup with only these two mods installed.

I would dearly love to be able to use them both but it appears for now that they are mutually exclusive.

EDIT: BoulderCo looks like the problem. Deleted it and it works fine. Not sure if that's a workaround or just better specificity.

Edited March 21, 2015 by LanceVader
Game loads fine if I get rid of BoulderCo in the KSRPC pack.

Looks like I spoke too soon. It crashed again on startup, halfway through loading.
